      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CRYSTAL MOONBEAM (4) was prominent on the corner and fought on well over 1100m at this track, beaten 1.5 lengths fresh from a spell. Has the rail and more up her sleeve and fitter she can go one better. LIVE ON LOVE (1) opened this campaign last start beaten 2 lengths, over 1100m at this track, as a $3.2 favourite. Impressed just missing here prior on debut, and a big run is on the cards. SUPER SNIPPY (3) got closer at Launceston over this trip and Byrne Burke is reunited. Draws low and he can get into the finish. LADY FERN (5) has some ability but has been cruelled by wide gates her last two. Maps better today and has trialled well since last seen. In the mix. MASTER OF MISCHIEF (6) was better here last time and won't be far away on that effort.",
